Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and SW-Checklist Completed across all variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time it takes to complete SW-Checklist Completed after Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Time elapsed from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-Checklist Completed in variants that include both activities
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Checklist Completed compared to the total time of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in the same cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Checklist Completed and the end of the case

Name: Minimum waiting time to SW-Checklist Completed after the occurrence of SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average time from SW-Checklist Completed to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Checklist Completed and the subsequent activity in each variant where it appears
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-Checklist Completed and the end of the case

Name: Total time for SW-Checklist Completed in cases that end with SW-EIC Reject versus cases that proceed to SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and the end of case where activity 'SW-EIC Reject occurs

Name: Time from SW-Checklist Completed to SW-Initial Reviewer Selection in variants where both activities occur consecutively
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Average time it takes SW-Checklist Completed to be performed after Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission in relevant variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Checklist Completed and Manuscript Export Succeeded when the latter precedes it
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Cycle time of SW-Checklist Completed in submissions that trigger Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded versus those that do not
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and the end of case where activity 'Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded occurs

Name: Total time from SW-Checklist Completed to the final decision activity (e.g., SW-EIC Accept, SW-EIC Reject, SW-EIC Major Revision) in each variant
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'
